channel.title: ourfishfamily
channel.description: Welcome to our Fish Family blog and our family gallery. Add us to your bookmarks and stay a while… grab a beer or a glass of wine, kick up your feet, splurge on a tub of bon-bons (yummo), sit back, relax and enjoy — Happy Reading! M&M

item.title: happy new year
item.dc:creator: ourfishfamily
item.content:encoded: A day spent with my favorite people at one of my favorite spots. Such a fun time - clear skies as far as the eye could see, warm sunshine on our backs, smiles that wrapped our faces and a wild puppy. Great day!

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: 2022, please be good to us all!!!

item.title: rugby all club day
item.dc:creator: ourfishfamily
item.content:encoded:
Matilda's rugby club hosts a season kick-off event that she was excited to take part in this year. She helped run a few drill stations, played a pick up game, met up with a few of her teammates and brought home a swag shirt.

Fun day now, let the games begin!

The next day our neighbor sent a message that Matilda had made it onto the club Instagram account - she's famous!

item.title: booster-ed
item.dc:creator: ourfishfamily
item.content:encoded: Shots are never on the top of anyones list and the kids absolutely despise them. However, the place Mark found for their boosters was such a positive experience, we might have turned a corner with their views on shots... The ice pack on the arm was life changing (mental note for the future).

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: 3rd COVID shot - complete. Can this all be over now??!!

item.content:encoded: DLS hosted the MLK Classic basketball tournament. Teams from around the Bay Area came to play. Each of the four basketball teams played a game and all attended the Varsity game to support the program. So fun seeing Mitch in the DLS media guide!
